<section class="privacy">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-deco" aria-hidden="true">🔒</div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2>Vos spots restent secrets</h2>
        <p>
          Un coin rare que vous voulez garder pour vous ? À chaque partage, un simple bouton décide
          si les coordonnées GPS sont incluses ou non. Vos lieux ne quittent votre téléphone
          que si vous le décidez.
        </p>
        <div class="demo" aria-label="Exemple de contrôle de partage GPS">
          <div class="demo-row">
            <span class="demo-label">📍 Partager la localisation</span>
            <div class="toggle" role="switch" aria-checked="false" aria-label="Localisation désactivée">
              <div class="thumb"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="demo-hint">✓ La photo est partagée, pas l'endroit</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .privacy {
    padding: var(--section-py) 0;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-900) 0%, #0e3b20 100%);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px);
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -80px;
    right: -80px;
    width: 360px;
    height: 360px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.1) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .card-deco {
    font-size: 4rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3));
  }

  .card-body {
    color: var(--white);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    opacity: 0.82;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  /* Démo toggle */
  .demo {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
  }

  .demo-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .demo-label {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .toggle {
    width: 44px;
    height: 24px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 2px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .thumb {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .demo-hint {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    opacity: 0.65;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .card {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .demo { text-align: left; }
  }
</style>
